    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. But if the risk is \"remote\" like you said, isn't it a bit reckless to just shrug it off and keep racing ahead? Like, isn't there a moral obligation to treat even a small chance of extinction as something that actually requires serious, heavy-handed regulation right now?",
